<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_ddae761f-42b7-4f1f-a0e2-cca6b317914c" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>B7P3</sptc><title id="_db27c272-23c7-43da-add5-5f0ccff996c2">Access</title><archive-num>2019: BP6.2</archive-num><clause-variation href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/10755_0.3.0.xml" variation="TAS" variation-type="REPLACE">TAS REPLACE Clause</clause-variation><subclause id="_6862c942-33eb-41b3-87c8-c6da830af859" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_ac06b567-bcb7-43f8-a99a-977ac3ef1f99">SubClause</title><num/><p>Access must be provided to components of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/4891_0.8.0.xml#_a8d909a0-d649-477d-a969-848c9187c05d" id="_b3112b80-f469-449e-956e-36683b97f423" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">rainwater storage</xref> that require maintenance or replacement, including mechanical devices and controls.</p></subclause><callout id="_8a44b324-192c-41f0-98f2-ff3d59061f95"><callout-type ncc-info-type="exemption"/><p>B7P3 does not apply to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1463_0.4.0.xml#_fb3536f6-7ee5-4a29-a4da-402a8e1168dc" id="_0cc96f1c-144d-4393-87c1-4482050aea76" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">sites</xref> not provided with a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1250_0.7.0.xml#_762d6a54-e28c-400b-b9c5-5fceac019a05" id="_f7a9b1fb-4b19-4888-ae5d-b448818e185b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">drinking water</xref> service by a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1376_4.2.0.xml#_12d6153c-4986-4856-80c0-e21bb57af12f" id="_0a80a28f-f353-4748-ade6-1e5f5c0ab1a7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Network Utility Operator</xref>.</p></callout><callout id="_bc060e97-a6e8-43f5-8b6f-fecb61e70428"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>Access to mechanical components may require removal of an access panel, cover, door, or similar obstruction.</p></callout></clause>